.el .ds Aq '
.TH devin-cloud-drs-run 1  "run " 
.SH NAME
devin\-cloud\-drs\-run \- Run a shell command inside a sandbox session
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin cloud drs run\fR <\fB\-\-devin\-id\fR> <\fB\-\-command\fR> [\fB\-\-timeout\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Run a shell command inside a sandbox session
.PP
Executes the command on the remote sandbox and blocks until it completes (or the timeout is reached).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-devin\-id\fR \fI<DEVIN_ID>\fR
Devin session ID (e.g. `devin\-abc123...`)
.TP
\fB\-\-command\fR \fI<COMMAND>\fR
Shell command to execute
.TP
\fB\-\-timeout\fR \fI<TIMEOUT>\fR [default: 600]
Timeout in seconds (server\-side)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
